P_HTM[225]='******118*. ‘‘Dvinnaṃ, bhikkhave, āsavā na vaḍḍhanti. Katamesaṃ dvinnaṃ? Yo ca avinaye avinayasaññī, yo ca vinaye vinayasaññī. Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dvinnaṃ āsavā na vaḍḍhantī’’ti.*';
P_HTM[226]='*Bālavaggo pañcamo.*';
